they are omitted. The five retained models span the spectrum the paper
describes, from realistically structured (\code{SRL_GPT}) to strongly
"over-coherent" (\code{SRL_Gemini}, \code{SRL_Claude}), making the set useful for
demonstrating and comparing network estimators.
